review: I tried So Delicious non-dairy yogurt for the first time.The texture is creamy after stirring.It does appear a bit watery when the lid is removed but that disappears with stirring.The flavor is delicious and the color a lovely shade of purple...not the tan or gray color of some non-dairy yogurts.I will definitely be buying more So Delicious non-dairy yogurt.

title: Thin Consistency for SoDelicious Fruit Flavors
review: I reviewed the strawberry and basically said the same thing. The consistency of the fruit flavors of this brand are thin/pretty liquidy. The flavor is good, but I will most likely only buy these on very rare occasions, such as when I need an extra dollar something to reach free shipping.
